            bindings = <
                       &kp Q               &kp W           &kp E      &kp R             &kp T        &kp Y          &kp U      &kp I         &kp O                 &kp P
                       &kp A               &kp S           &kp D      &kp F             &kp G        &kp H          &kp J      &kp K         &kp L                 &kp SEMICOLON
&mt LEFT_SHIFT ESCAPE  &mt LEFT_CONTROL Z  &mt LEFT_ALT X  &kp C      &kp V             &kp B        &kp N          &kp M      &kp COMMA     &mt RIGHT_ALT PERIOD  &mt RCTRL SLASH  &mt RIGHT_SHIFT SQT
                                                           &lt 1 TAB  &kp LEFT_COMMAND  &kp SPACE    &kp BACKSPACE  &lt 3 TAB  &lt 2 DELETE
